title: Trendi Handbags 7/28: 2 Chainz x Rick Ross, MGK, Emmys, Shark Attack

description:
On this edition of Trendi Handbags Miles and Laci discuss the next Verzuz battle between 2 Chainz and Rick Ross, Machine Gun Kelly and Megan Fox are officially dating, many awesome people and shows were nominated for Emmy awards, and someone has passed due to Shark attack off the coast of Maine.
